<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans und Albrecht von Wolfstein zu Sulzbürg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Fritz Strobel, Diener der Stadt, wegen des von Michael Prentlein, Richter zu Sulzbürg, beschlagnahmten Viehs der Armleute zu Haslach des Heilig-Geist-Spitals zu Nürnberg und des verstorbenen Heinrich Grabner, Bürger zu Nürnberg, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_290" id="144v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_290_r1l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hanſen vnd <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l2">vom wolfſtein cʒu der <expan>Solcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_290_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Hans vnd <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> / Als wir nehſt den <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Huber </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener cʒu ew geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des vihs wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l5">als der prentlein <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> d </del> Richter des 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Spita </del> Newenſpitals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l6">hie vnd des <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Grabn<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers <expan>ſelıge<ex>n</ex></expan> kinde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l7"> <expan>Armenlewte<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu Hohenhaſlach <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat 
<del rend="strikethrough">Darümb </del> Alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l9">ſenden vvir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_290_r1l8"><expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erb fricʒen Strobell <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıener mit ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l10">dauon cʒureden / vnd bıten ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleiſʒıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> / vvaʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l11"><expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> fricʒ Strobel in <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache cʒu diſem mal an ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l12">werb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen / daʒ Jr Jm des <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_290_r1l13">darümb gütlıch von ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tıge<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_290" id="144v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen und <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> vom
                        Wolfstein czu der <expan>Solczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Hans und
                        <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, als wir nehst den
                            <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Huber, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, czu ew gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des vihs wegen, als
                        der Prentlein, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> richter, des newenspitals hie und
                        des <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Grabn<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers,
                                <expan>selige<ex>n</ex></expan> kinde
                            <expan>armenlewte<ex>n</ex></expan> czu Hohenhaslach
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, also senden wir
                                    <add><expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan></add> czu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> erb Friczen Strobell,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, mit ew davon czu reden und
                        biten ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiszikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>, waz der
                            <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> Fricz Strobel in
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache czu disem mal an ew werb von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wegen, daz ir im des
                                <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und in darümb gütlich von ew
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tige<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
